Package room

Class Room

  • java.lang.Object
    • room.Room
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents the rooms that events could take place in. The number of people that can be in the room is represented by capacity. The actual number of the room is represented by roomNumber. Rooms can have some number of computers, a projector, tables, and chairs.
